      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the veg is cooking, peel and finely dice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Finely dice your <strong>apple[s]</strong> (skin on) and discard the core[s]</p><p>Heat a pot over a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> diced red onion</strong> and <strong>apple</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> </strong>cook for 4-5 min or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
