    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a baking tray (or two!) with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p><p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong>, then unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Place the <strong>pastry</strong> on the tray, then add your<strong> meat-free sausage roll mix</strong> and lay it down the centre of the pastry in a sausage shape</p><p>Tip: You may need to make multiple if cooking for more than 2!</p>",
      "order": 5,
